                            <comment id="14630581" author="junrao" created="Fri, 17 Jul 2015 00:17:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch. +1 and committed to trunk.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch handles the case when the full list of partitions is not returned in TopicMetadataResponse. However, the broker should always return all partitions in a topic in TopicMetadataResponse. We need to figure out why this is not always true. So, leaving this jira open.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
